<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 22 at 2:02PM EST  by NWS Blacksburg</headline>
<description>...Black ice expected for tonight into Sunday morning...
Temperatures should fall into the teens tonight, which will cause
any melted snow or ice to refreeze. Roads, bridges, and sidewalks
will develop black ice and may become hazardous. Use caution if
driving or walking during tonight into tomorrow morning.</description>
